  "description": "A close-up, ground-level view of a weathered piece of driftwood lying on a sandy beach. The wood is dark brown and heavily textured, showing signs of erosion and age. Behind the driftwood, there's a blurred background of sand dunes covered in sparse, dry vegetation. The dunes create a rolling landscape leading towards a pale blue sky with faint contrails from aircraft. The sand appears grainy and slightly damp, with subtle patterns created by wind or footprints. The overall image evokes a sense of coastal serenity and the natural processes of decay and renewal.",
